reviewText: I have been a big fan of this television series ever since I discovered it from "Bookworm Bunch." Also, I really like that the main character was a certain member of a school talent show known as the "master of ceremonies."

My kids love Timothy Goes to School books and loved the tv show. The show deals with children in elementary school and my kids could really realte to the characters. Unfortunatley it is not on tv anymore so we bought this video. The seller was very fast in shipping it out and the video is great.
